trans-unit.source: Provides data for the known, but unreferenced, object found in an encoded SOAP XML stream during deserialization.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder data for kjente, men urefererte,-objekt funnet i en kodet SOAP-XML-strømmen under deserialisering.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the UnreferencedObjectEventArgs class, see the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject> event of the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om klassen UnreferencedObjectEventArgs se <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject>hendelsen for <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer>.</xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> </xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject> event occurs only when you call the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.Deserialize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject>inntreffer bare når du kaller den <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.Deserialize%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.Deserialize%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject>

trans-unit.source: For more information about handling events, see [Events Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om behandling av hendelser [oversikt over aktiviteter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.UnreferencedObjectEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.UnreferencedObjectEventArgs"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: A unique string used to identify the unreferenced object.
trans-unit.target: En unik Formatstrengen som brukes til å identifisere det urefererte objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the ID of the object.
Use the UnreferencedId property when you need to know when more than one object raises the event.
trans-unit.target: Bruke egenskapen UnreferencedId når du trenger å vite når flere objekter opphøyer hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The property allows you to distinguish between multiple instances of unreferenced objects.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen lar deg å skille mellom flere forekomster av ubrukte objekter.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the UnreferencedId property, see the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject> event.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om egenskapen UnreferencedId den <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject>hendelsen.</xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject>

trans-unit.source: Gets the deserialized, but unreferenced, object.
The UnreferencedObject can be cast to the known type if examining its properties is required.
trans-unit.target: UnreferencedObject kan endres til kjent type Hvis undersøker egenskapene er påkrevd.

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject> event for more information about the UnreferencedObject property.
trans-unit.target: Se den <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject>hendelsen for mer informasjon om egenskapen UnreferencedObject.</xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer.UnreferencedObject>
